name: My Lady Jane
overview: Gird your loins for the tragic tale of Lady Jane Grey, the young Tudor noblewoman who was Queen of England for nine days and then beheaded, back in good ol’ 1553. Actually... f*ck that. We’re retelling history the way it should have happened: the damsel in distress saves herself. This is an epic tale of true love and high adventure set in an alt-universe of action, history, fantasy, comedy, romance, and rompy-pompy. Buckle up.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Are you ready for an epic tale of true love, high adventure, regicidal maniacs, deadpan heroism, devious intrigues, swashbuckling swordfights, a soupçon of magical realism and oodles of yearning, banter and undeniable chemistry? Of course you are. Welcome to My Lady Jane.

episodes.name: Who'll Be the Next in Line?
episodes.overview: Meet Lady Jane Grey. Brilliant, but more usefully, beautiful. And about to have the worst day of her life. (So far.)

episodes.name: Wild Thing
episodes.overview: What’s worse: when you have the raging horn for an unmitigated scoundrel? Or when he has a deep dark secret that could get you both killed?

episodes.name: With a Girl Like You
episodes.overview: Midnight quests in the woods, spanking, feasts, duels, murder and snogging. This episode has it all.

episodes.name: Bluebird Is Dead
episodes.overview: Jane is Queen and people keep trying to kill her. Pass the wine.

episodes.name: I'm Gonna Change the World
episodes.overview: Mary is coming for Jane’s crown. Frances is coming for Guildford. And the nobility is coming to get hammered at Jane’s Coronation Banquet.

episodes.name: I Feel Free
episodes.overview: Missing: the roguish consort to the Queen of England. If you have any idea as to his whereabouts, do let us know.

episodes.name: Another Girl, Another Planet
episodes.overview: Jane is on trial for treason. And Guildford, Edward and Fitz are determined to save her. Typical men.
